STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Petitioner,
v.
Joshua M. GREEN, Defendant-Respondent. C-611 September Term 2017
080002 Supreme Court of New Jersey. February 9, 2018

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-004392-13 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
